msgid "Scenario II: Return to The Miskatonic Museum"
msgstr "冒险II：重返博物馆之夜"

msgid "Set the “Exhibit Hall” locations aside as a separate 6 card “Exhibit Deck.” To do this, perform the following:"
msgstr "将“展厅”地点组成6张卡牌的展厅牌堆。请按以下步骤执行："

msgid "Gather the 8 “Exhibit Hall” locations. Set Exhibit Hall <i>(Restricted Hall)</i> aside and randomly remove 2 Exhibit Hall locations from the game."
msgstr "找出所有8张展厅地点。将展厅<i>(禁止入内)</i>放在一边，并随机将2个展厅地点移出游戏。"

msgid "Shuffle the Exhibit Hall <i>(Restricted Hall)</i> and 2 other random Exhibit Hall locations together to form the bottom 3 cards of the Exhibit Deck, unrevealed side faceup."
msgstr "将展厅<i>(禁止入内)</i>和其他随机2张展厅混洗，未揭示面朝上，放在展厅牌堆底部。"

msgid ""
"For the duration of this scenario, the following additional rule applies:\n"
"\"While an investigator is resolving the text on agenda 1b and agenda 2b, the <b>Forced</b> ability on the next agenda in the agenda deck is considered to be active.\"\n"
"Attach the Return to The Miskatonic Museum scenario reference card to the scenario reference card as a reminder."
msgstr ""
"这场冒险期间，请遵守以下额外规则：\n"
"“调查员结算密谋1b和密谋2b上的文本时，密谋牌堆中下一张密谋卡上的<b>强制</b>能力视为启动。”\n"
"将重返博物馆之夜冒险参考卡叠加到原冒险参考卡，作为提醒。\""
